00:10:02,789 --> 00:10:07,368
KUberako biguha ahantu hafatika
uhera ufata ibyemezo bijyanye

178
00:10:07,848 --> 00:10:12,024
aho kampani yawe izahangana,
n'uko izahangana

179
00:10:12,024 --> 00:10:13,719
N'iyo mishinga.

180
00:10:13,719 --> 00:10:16,107
Akenshi ba rwiyemezamirimo
baza kundeba bakaguga, bati

181
00:10:16,107 --> 00:10:19,432
"Ntago dufite abo duhanganye,
ibicuruzwa byacu birimo agashya cyane

182
00:10:19,432 --> 00:10:21,968
katarabaho na rimwe
mu isoko."

183
00:10:22,418 --> 00:10:27,072
Hanyuma nkavuga nti" ibyo birashoboka gusa mugihe
utarakoze akazi kawe

184
00:10:27,072 --> 00:10:28,457
Nea nk'uko bikwiye."

185
00:10:28,457 --> 00:10:32,248
Jyerageza, rwose kumva
abakiriya bawe n'abo muhanganye.

186
00:10:32,248 --> 00:10:37,295
kubera ko n'udushya hano hanze
tuba dufite ibintu byadusimbura

187
00:10:37,295 --> 00:10:41,926
biri kwita kubikenewe 
n'abakiriya bawe.

188
00:10:42,566 --> 00:10:45,413
Hari ibintu byasimbura icyo gicuruzwa,
n'ibindi bijya gusa nabyo byaba bihari.

189
00:10:46,153 --> 00:10:49,290
Kuvuga ngo "ntago dufite
abo duhanganye"

190
00:10:49,290 --> 00:10:53,016
akenshi ni ikimenyetso
ko utakoze

191
00:10:53,016 --> 00:10:54,706
Umukoro wawe neza.

192
00:10:54,706 --> 00:11:00,488
Rero fata ubub busesenguzi bw'abo muhanganye
nk'ikintu gikomeye kumutima wawe.

193
00:11:00,678 --> 00:11:04,845
Kandi ugerageze gusobanukirwa "aya ni 
amahirwe mbonye yo kwiga byinshi

194
00:11:04,845 --> 00:11:07,272
kuri kampani yanjye n'isoko."

195
00:11:08,012 --> 00:11:11,716
Ikindi gishimishije kandi
ni ukureba mubakiriya b'abo muhanganye.

196
00:11:11,716 --> 00:11:15,036
Abo aribo, uko bafite
ibice bitandukanye mu isoko,

197
00:11:15,036 --> 00:11:17,190
n'ibyo bacuruza kuri buri gice.

198
00:11:17,190 --> 00:11:20,648
Imbaraga nyinshi z'abo muhanganye n'integenke
zaba nk'uko abakiriya babibona.

199
00:11:20,648 --> 00:11:24,301
Niba hari bakiriya,
b'igihe cyirecyire bari kwitaho

200
00:11:24,301 --> 00:11:28,763
bitakoroheraguhita wigarurira 
ngo ubashyire kuri kampani yawe.

201
00:11:28,763 --> 00:11:31,348
Cyeretse ufite ibintu byiza,
bibereka agaciro kenshi.

202
00:11:31,858 --> 00:11:34,137
niba harabayeho kwiyongera 
kw'abakiriya

203
00:11:34,137 --> 00:11:36,793
Kuko ibi nabyo ari ikimenyetso 
cy'ingenzi cyerekana niba

204
00:11:36,793 --> 00:11:39,370
NIba bafite ikintu gikurura abantu cyane
bashobora gushyira ku isoko.

205
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:44,694
Kuburyo ushobora kurundi ruhande
ubufatanije n'ibyo waganiriye n'abakiriya

206
00:11:44,694 --> 00:11:47,677
Ushobora kubisobanukirwa neza
uganiriye n'abakiriya.

207
00:11:47,677 --> 00:11:50,171
Uko batekereza n'ibyo 
bitaho

208
00:11:50,171 --> 00:11:54,873
Ariko wanareba za raporo z'isoko
n'andi moko ya za raporo

209
00:11:54,873 --> 00:11:56,218
kujyirango bigufashe gusobanukirwa

210
00:11:56,218 --> 00:12:00,208
"Ese nigute,
ibintu biri guhinduka mu isoko?" kandi se

211
00:12:00,208 --> 00:12:03,363
abo duhanganye bab ahari
bari gutanga ikintu

212
00:12:03,363 --> 00:12:05,303
gishimishije cyane kubakiriya?"

213
00:12:05,303 --> 00:12:09,370
Iki ni ikintu cy'ingenzi muguha ishusho
y'igicuruzwa cyawe.

214
00:12:09,370 --> 00:12:11,550
ndetse na gahunda zawe z'imenyekanisha.

215
00:12:11,550 --> 00:12:14,845
Byose bikakugeza
kubintu bitatu by'ingenzi.

216
00:12:14,845 --> 00:12:18,598
Icymbere, ni iki wakwigira
kubantu muhanganye ngo ukore neza kurushaho?

217
00:12:18,878 --> 00:12:25,005
icya kabiri, ni icyi abo muhanganye batari gukora
jye ndi gukora? cyangwa nteganya gukora?

218
00:12:25,545 --> 00:12:29,695
na, ni iki bari gukora
nk'uko nanjye ngikora?

219
00:12:29,695 --> 00:12:33,757
Bityo ni ureba kuri ibi bintu bitatu--
bikwereka ahantu

220
00:12:33,757 --> 00:12:38,787
ho gukosora, n'aho ushobora
kurusha abo muhanganye.

221
00:12:39,937 --> 00:12:41,279
By'umwihariko mugihe cyo gutegura,
wavuga uti,

222
00:12:41,279 --> 00:12:44,799
Nzategura umushinga muburyo,
n'igicuruzwa cyanjye muburyo

223
00:12:44,799 --> 00:12:49,168
nzarwanya bo duhanganye
mpereye aho bafite intege nke."

224
00:12:50,288 --> 00:12:53,588
Ariko nano wibuke ko abakiriya bagikeneye
ko uha agaciro urwego

225
00:12:53,588 --> 00:12:56,619
uri kugerageza gutsindaho hano.

226
00:12:57,269 --> 00:13:01,412
Hanyuma ibyo uri gukora kimwe n'abo 
muhanganye wavuga uti

227
00:13:01,412 --> 00:13:07,118
"ese nshobora kujyira akantu nongeramo,
bintandukanye n'abandi?"

228
00:13:07,118 --> 00:13:11,283
kuburyo abakiriya bazavuga bati,
"Iki ni ikintu cy'akarusho umushinga wawe

229
00:13:11,283 --> 00:13:14,364
uri gutanga ntigeze mbona,
muyindi mishinga muhanganye.

230
00:13:14,364 --> 00:13:16,680
Bityo ngiye guhitamo igicuruzwa cyawe."

231
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:19,941
Muri make, ibyo twaganiriyeho
muri aka gace--

232
00:13:19,941 --> 00:13:22,732
ni ibintu bisobanutse,
gusa bisobanuye gukora cyane.

233
00:13:23,092 --> 00:13:26,456
Ariko ndabasaba gukora aka kazi,
mukore imirimo nk'iyo

234
00:13:26,456 --> 00:13:30,503
kuko bikwereka
ishingiro ry'ahantu ugiye gushinga umushinga.

235
00:13:31,423 --> 00:13:35,677
Akenshi abantu baravuga bati "yewe,  gahunda y'
umushinga yawe ntago yumva neza

236
00:13:35,677 --> 00:13:38,199
ntizakomeza kubaho 
nimara kubonana n'abakiriya bwa mbere."

237
00:13:38,199 --> 00:13:41,895
Ibyo biba gusa iyo utigeze uvugana
n'umukiriya mbere.

238
00:13:41,895 --> 00:13:47,188
Ukeneye gusobanukirwa icyo abakiriya bawe
bashaka ndetse n'abo muhanganye

239
00:13:47,188 --> 00:13:50,918
kugirango ubashe kuzana umushinga
ubushimishije ndetssse mwiza.

240
00:13:50,918 --> 00:13:54,052
Aha rero hakaba ariho
iki gice cyigufasha.

241
00:13:54,052 --> 00:13:55,968
Gukora ubushakashatsi kku isoko,
no gusesengura abo muhanganye.

242
00:13:55,968 --> 00:13:59,908
Rero twarebye muri aka gave
ibintu bibiri by'ingenzi

243
00:13:59,908 --> 00:14:03,167
wakora
kugirango usobanukirwa abakiriya neza

244
00:14:03,167 --> 00:14:06,666
Ukanabasha kumva neza
abo muhanganye.

245
00:14:07,646 --> 00:14:11,740
Uzabijyerageze, mfite amatsiko
yo kumenya icyo mwigiyemo.

246
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:13,001
Amahirwe masa!
